				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Ngo%E1%BA%A1n/B%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A1t-man/poem-wQ1dbLeqgRULCReg03LX3Q">Bồ tát man - 菩薩蠻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Ngo%E1%BA%A1n/author-uWWMt6j8c6UoM1tDLnF61Q">Nguỵ Ngoạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Cung-ngh%C4%A9-Gia-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87n-thi%C3%AAn-hoa-thi%E1%BA%BFp-t%E1%BB%AD-th%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-48keoyuc54SEX6hm1mxcyA">Cung nghĩ Gia Thành điện thiên hoa thiếp tử thất thủ kỳ 4 - 恭擬嘉成殿天花帖子七首其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Huy-Chi/H%C3%A1n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-v%C3%A3n-b%E1%BA%A1c/poem-b7bIm68islVqEWAHVgn54Q">Hán Dương vãn bạc - 漢陽晚泊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Huy-Chi/author-_Y_ZwtenVmhfHtsbT4YCdQ">Dương Huy Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BB%99-b%E1%BB%99-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-B%C3%ACnh-Nam-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khoa-T%C3%A2n-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-c%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-e-B1-j6bWizmnwNlZDYBYg">Hoạ hộ bộ thượng thư Bình Nam Nguyễn Khoa Tân tiên sinh cửu nhật nguyên vận - 和戶部尚書屏南阮科濱先生九日原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A2u-B%E1%BA%A3o-Quy%C3%AAn/Ho%C3%A0i-Trinh-Nh%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%89/poem-Cd-F00pVbnueBw9HxokPHA">Hoài Trinh Như tỉ - 懷貞如姊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A2u-B%E1%BA%A3o-Quy%C3%AAn/author-816JJmH1ANKAym6VLMPV8Q">Mâu Bảo Quyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/Khai-Nguy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1-kh%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%89nh-t%E1%BA%A3o-c%E1%BA%A3nh-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-YRhZLA7fc9DOHzvrVZVoDw">Khai Nguyên tự khách tỉnh tảo cảnh tức sự - 開元寺客省早景即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/author-YaU63-B8n1CAEl8OjKg7AQ">Bì Nhật Hưu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Long-Th%C3%A0nh-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-uAMZgXgJMLszZtZYKc6Wmg">Long Thành trúc chi từ kỳ 1 - 龍城竹枝詞其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/Sinh-tra-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-S7v5E_7ENdSDkZWf-yQ-nQ">Sinh tra tử - 生查子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-pie5Fia6OX3GJydppNrLBw">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tứ đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第四段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-2-T%E1%BB%91ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-gia/poem-M-50xx2ow4YFv2TP3AmR1w">Vịnh hoài cổ tích kỳ 2 - Tống Ngọc gia - 詠懷古跡其二－宋玉家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
